{"tid":1537630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究 竟 係 咪 想 要 831 cctv? 快入","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T19:17:20.000Z","uid":186851,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"85ba27112d1eb4ab89b76b87aab7a65458af35b5","tid":1537630,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"律師建議］ 緊急 請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n831太子站當日有份俾人打嘅市民，請盡快聯絡律師做民事訴訟(personal injuries)，向法庭申請要地鐵攞CCTV。<br />\n<br />\n一定要快，如果過咗期限，地鐵話自動洗咗啲CCTV，到時就真係冇人知道太子發生過咩事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n註：其實唔止身體受傷，心靈受創都可以告。當日喺現場目擊事件，造成精神痛苦，都可以嘗試用 secondary victim （非直接受害人）去追討。最後告唔告得入唔係最重要，目的係令多啲人有權拎CCTV，還原真相⚠️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟 98190979<br />\n民陣 65499452<br />\n民權觀察 94632945<br />\n伍展邦律師行 26081400<br />\n<br />\n推呀！！唔想有人抄車，但更加唔想抄左車但冇人知！！黑警一定要還債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追究到底！"},{"pid":"539191987f82edb250b85346b211916b645c1614","tid":1537630,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9418e6cb801e624321c87aba3291c9a9307bfa96","tid":1537630,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:53:37.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"87d4faa8240b0bd47a857daf66510e2d9524d98f","tid":1537630,"uid":130076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c90dd9e304f3ea18500a8d06515c5398705b37d5","tid":1537630,"uid":130076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:54:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d38969d2b26d9942e6c0599c0adf534d8fb66fbd","tid":1537630,"uid":241328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"11dc13861b4f3adde0853fdaf89f2714ada90b25","tid":1537630,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9db5157f129a5714fd0b362ac80e74b20375fb74","tid":1537630,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"3e7d7d897a5bd2bb5f4704ba35f3ecc442f9bc0b","tid":1537